<item>
            <title>[MNG-895] Profile resources not merged with main POM</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-895</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Profile resources are not merged with resources specified in the main POM, e.g.:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;project&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 ...&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;build&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;resources&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;resource&amp;gt;a&amp;lt;/resource&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/resources&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;/build&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;profiles&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;profile&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     ...&lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;build&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       &amp;lt;resources&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;resource&amp;gt;b&amp;lt;/resource&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       &amp;lt;/resources&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;/build&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     ...&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/profile&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;/profiles&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 ...&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/project&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The effective resources block should consist of both &apos;a&apos; and &apos;b&apos; when the profile is activated, but currently &apos;b&apos; overrides &apos;a&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
