                            <comment id="14408802" author="jdcasey" created="Fri, 16 Sep 2005 11:24:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-895&quot; title=&quot;Profile resources not merged with main POM&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MNG-895&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MNG-895&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is the root cause of MNG-881.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14408767" author="brettporter" created="Fri, 23 Sep 2005 19:41:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;note that this will also affect filters as they are not inherited at present for the same reason&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
